\noindent {\bf Stage 2: Precision-oriented Scrutinization}. Given a high-recall list of object candidates from Stage 1, the second stage uses conservative techniques to corroborate or prune objects. We employ novel techniques to identify high-confidence objects and their best support passages, and use them to re-assess lower-confidence candidates.